RewriteEngine on

## Global
RewriteRule ^([a-zA-Z]{1,20})$   									index.php?page=$1 [L]
RewriteRule ^([a-zA-Z]{1,20})/$   									index.php?page=$1 [L]
RewriteRule ^([a-zA-Z]{1,20})/([a-zA-Z]{1,20})$   					index.php?page=$1&action=$2 [L]
RewriteRule ^([a-zA-Z]{1,20})/([a-zA-Z]{1,20})/([a-zA-Z0-9]{1,20})$   	index.php?page=$1&action=$2&params=$3 [L]